*evolution-3.8.1 (14 Apr 2013)

  14 Apr 2013; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> +evolution-3.8.1.ebuild:
  Version bump

  11 Apr 2013; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> evolution-3.6.3.ebuild,
  evolution-3.6.4.ebuild, evolution-3.8.0.ebuild:
  3.6.2-r1 was keyworded on arm, but later versions dropped it again by error
  leading to repoman failure with gnome-base/gnome-extra-apps

  31 Mar 2013; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> evolution-3.8.0.ebuild:
  Adapt to libsoup-2.42 dropping gnome USE and splitting (#463702)

