  Add ~ia64, wrt bug #449220

  31 Dec 2012; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> evolution-3.6.2-r1.ebuild:
  Add ~ppc64, wrt bug #449220

  24 Dec 2012; Alexandre Rostovtsev <tetromino@gentoo.org>
  evolution-2.32.3-r1.ebuild, evolution-3.4.4.ebuild,
  evolution-3.6.2-r1.ebuild:
  Depend on evolution-data-server with the same major/minor version (bug
  #448350).

*evolution-3.6.2-r1 (19 Dec 2012)

  19 Dec 2012; Alexandre Rostovtsev <tetromino@gentoo.org>
  -files/evolution-3.2.1-reorder-mx-clutter-gtk.patch,
  -evolution-3.2.3-r1.ebuild, -files/evolution-3.2.3-g_thread_init.patch,
  -files/evolution-3.2.3-gmodule-explicit.patch,
  -files/evolution-3.2.3-gtkhtml-4.4.patch, +evolution-3.6.2-r1.ebuild:
  Version bump for gnome-3.6. Drop old.

  26 Nov 2012; Alexandre Rostovtsev <tetromino@gentoo.org>
  evolution-3.2.3-r1.ebuild, evolution-3.4.4.ebuild:
  Don't call PYTHON before python_pkg_setup.

  26 Nov 2012; Alexandre Rostovtsev <tetromino@gentoo.org>
  evolution-2.32.3-r1.ebuild, evolution-3.2.3-r1.ebuild,
  evolution-3.4.4.ebuild:
  Fix build failure with python3 as system interpreter (bug #444694, thanks to
  Jens Kasten).

  17 Nov 2012; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> -evolution-2.32.3.ebuild,
  evolution-2.32.3-r1.ebuild:
  Fix building with latest automake dropping last -Werror instance we missed
  before (#442242 by evgenn), show message for changing browser only when people
  don't have gnome-default-applications-properties provider. Remove old.

  27 Oct 2012; Alexandre Rostovtsev <tetromino@gentoo.org>
  evolution-3.4.4.ebuild:
  Requires gtk+-3.4 (bug #433896, thanks to Jaakko Perttilä).

  17 Oct 2012; Alexandre Rostovtsev <tetromino@gentoo.org>
  -evolution-2.32.2-r3.ebuild, evolution-2.32.3.ebuild,
  evolution-2.32.3-r1.ebuild, -evolution-3.2.3.ebuild,
  evolution-3.2.3-r1.ebuild, -evolution-3.4.3.ebuild, evolution-3.4.4.ebuild:
  Drop useless USE=doc, it only regenerated documentation. Update license.
  Update homepage. Drop old.

  06 Oct 2012; Anthony G. Basile <blueness@gentoo.org> evolution-3.4.4.ebuild:
  keyword ~ppc, bug #437372

