*evolution-3.2.2 (16 Nov 2011)

  16 Nov 2011; Alexandre Rostovtsev <tetromino@gentoo.org>
  evolution-2.32.2-r3.ebuild, evolution-2.32.3.ebuild,
  evolution-2.32.3-r1.ebuild, -evolution-3.0.3.ebuild, +evolution-3.2.2.ebuild:
  Bump to 3.2.2 with assorted bugfixes. Drop old.
  Also, QA: eautoreconf should be before gnome2_src_prepare.

*evolution-3.2.1 (31 Oct 2011)

  31 Oct 2011; Alexandre Rostovtsev <tetromino@gentoo.org>
  evolution-2.32.2-r3.ebuild, evolution-2.32.3.ebuild,
  evolution-2.32.3-r1.ebuild, evolution-3.0.3.ebuild, +evolution-3.2.1.ebuild,
  +files/evolution-3.2.1-reorder-mx-clutter-gtk.patch, metadata.xml:
  Bump to 3.2.1 from the gnome overlay. Add a patch to fix building when
  clutter-gtk:0.10 is installed. Switch to EAPI4 and add a REQUIRED_USE. Update
  the CPPFLAGS sed for configure.ac changes.
  In addition, fix clutter dependencies in existing evolution ebuilds.

  30 Oct 2011; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> evolution-2.32.3.ebuild:
  alpha/ia64/sparc stable wrt #385699

  21 Oct 2011; Pawel Hajdan jr <phajdan.jr@gentoo.org> evolution-2.32.3.ebuild:
  x86 stable wrt bug #385699

  16 Oct 2011; Kacper Kowalik <xarthisius@gentoo.org> evolution-2.32.3.ebuild:
  ppc/ppc64 stable wrt #385699

  14 Oct 2011; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> evolution-2.32.3.ebuild:
  amd64 stable wrt #385699

*evolution-2.32.3-r1 (08 Oct 2011)

  08 Oct 2011; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> -evolution-2.32.2.ebuild,
  evolution-2.32.3.ebuild, +evolution-2.32.3-r1.ebuild:
  Drop connman support for version to be stabilized as it cannot go to stable
  yet, remove .la files, drop old.

  05 Oct 2011; Kacper Kowalik <xarthisius@gentoo.org>
  evolution-2.32.2-r3.ebuild:
  ppc/ppc64 stable wrt #369909

*evolution-3.0.3 (30 Sep 2011)

  30 Sep 2011; Nirbheek Chauhan <nirbheek@gentoo.org> +evolution-3.0.3.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  Add evolution-3, from gnome overlay for GNOME 3 (TODO: file bug for USE=map
  keywording)

  13 Aug 2011; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> evolution-2.32.2-r3.ebuild:
  alpha/ia64/sparc stable wrt #369909

  14 Jul 2011; Thomas Kahle <tomka@gentoo.org> evolution-2.32.2-r3.ebuild:
  x86 stable per bug 369909

  01 Jul 2011; Markos Chandras <hwoarang@gentoo.org>
  evolution-2.32.2-r3.ebuild:
  Stable on amd64 wrt bug #278255

  01 Jul 2011; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> evolution-2.32.2.ebuild:
  Drop *DISABLE_DEPRECATED* also in stable evolution.

  26 Jun 2011; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> evolution-2.32.2-r3.ebuild:
  Disable connman in stable candidate as it is not ready to stabilize yet.

