  05 Aug 2007; Mart Raudsepp <leio@gentoo.org> evolution-2.10.2.ebuild:
  Drop networkmanager IUSE, so that evolution-2.10 can be stabilized, while
  networkmanager isn't ready yet for stabilization. If you want networkmanager
  support in evolution, you should be able to just emerge it and evolution
  should pick it up over D-Bus regardless

